{
  "stem": "21319.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after that, they-- they closed-- the-- one of the-- the crematoriums, they-- they closed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they moved us to another camp, Lager [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "C.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Lager C.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they liquidated-- Lager B was in Birkenau, and the other camps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because they knew that the front are close by.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they-- so we were taken to Lager C.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this was even worse, because we didn't have even a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was no chance of a piece-- of water, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were Lager C until the-- you know-- and the gypsies-- there was a camp for the gypsies where they took one day and they put them all in the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were walking to [GERMAN], and they were-- and this were the same-- and they were going, the gypsies, with their-- they had the gypsies with their families and their children.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they were all-- whole thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then we find out that the whole-- the whole gypsy camp was completely annihilated with the children, with the mothers and fathers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were the only-- and I remember there were only some [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] religious Christian, you know-- I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were-- [INAUDIBLE], I don't remember, which were liquidated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But then they started to liquidate Auschwitz by December.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "December-- by January, slowly, because they knew that the Russians are already there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So the-- and we were the only group which was left, was the-- my group.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So in January 27, we were the last people from Auschwitz Birkenau who came out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After us, we-- they closed it, you see?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had no clothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I told you, we-- we walked for five days and five nights.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And for five days and five nights, we were in the-- the coal wagons.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
